{"type":"message","id":"ddc6afed","parentId":"f1ae126a","timestamp":"2026-06-08T07:59:13.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about `tiktok_product_trend` and `ali1688_similar_product` - these are NOT skills, they appear to be MCP tools from the sorftime-mcp server. The skill workshop shows no proposals, and from the exec output I can see all installed skills.\n\nThe user's table shows:\n- tiktok_product_trend: ❌ 不存在 (TikTok品类趋势扫描)\n- ali1688_similar_product: ❌ 不存在 (1688同款商品查询)\n\nThese are MCP tool names, not skill names. They would be part of the sorftime MCP server tools. The user seems to be asking if these are skills or MCP tools, and if the sorftime MCP is working well.\n\n\nSo to clarify: those two items are MCP tools from sorftime-mcp, not skills, and the user is asking whether the sorftime MCP is actually functional or not.\n","thinkingSignature":"18c80eac25247a4e7cfb9211e06e98f5f1a07313e06d9b4a6f4f086b436a6b01"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**不是 skill，是 MCP tool。**\n\n从你的表格看，`tiktok_product_trend`（TikTok品类趋势扫描）和 `ali1688_similar_product`（1688同款商品查询）是 **Sorftime MCP Server 提供的工具**，不是 skill。\n\n---\n\n**我目前安装的 skill 列表：**\n\n**本地 skills**（`~/.openclaw/skills/`）：\n`agent-browser`, `auto-updater`, `find-skills`, `skill-creator`, `spike`, `taskflow`, `taskflow-inbox-triage`, `lossless-claw`, `browser-automation`\n\n**OpenClaw 内置 skills**（`~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`）：\n`canvas`, `clawhub`, `github`, `healthcheck`, `mcporter`, `meme-maker`, `node-connect`, `node-inspect-debugger`, `python-debugpy`, `weather` 等\n\n**飞书插件 skills**（`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/`）：\n`feishu-bitable`, `feishu-calendar`, `feishu-channel-rules`, `feishu-create-doc`, `feishu-fetch-doc`, `feishu-im-read`, `feishu-task`, `feishu-troubleshoot`, `feishu-update-doc` 等\n\n**企业微信插件 skills**：\n`wecom-*` 系列（contact-lookup, doc-manager, edit-todo, get-todo-detail, get-todo-list, meeting-create, meeting-manage, meeting-query, msg, preflight, schedule, send-media, send-template-card, smartsheet-data, smartsheet-schema）\n\n---\n\n关于 Sorftime MCP——你说的对，这两个工具显示「不存在」，说明 Sorftime MCP Server 可能没有这两个工具，或者说 MCP 工具名称可能不是这两个。\n\n你之前用的 Sorftime API 是通过 `exec curl` 调用的，不是通过 MCP。你想让我查一下 Sorftime MCP 实际提供了哪些工具吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3551,"output":590,"cacheRead":51701,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780905534293,"responseId":"0675a93f16e9f03a1f3d8a616db0439c"}}
