{"type":"message","id":"fdb120a6","parentId":"519c088b","timestamp":"2026-06-08T09:02:33.961Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is expressing frustration about:\n1. The time it's taking to get the Sorftime MCP integration working properly\n2. They want a clear SOP that can deliver results - 10 products per week entering their system, with quality products that can be tested\n3. Simply dumping all selected products into the Feishu table isn't useful - they can't track what's been tested\n\nLet me think about what's actually going on here. Looking at my MEMORY.md:\n- The core strategy is \"趋势黑马拦截 + 三级漏斗验证 + 1688利润终选\"\n- But the user is saying the actual approach should be simpler: follow what's already selling well (跟品), don't over-complicate with 3-step verification since hot products have already been validated\n\n\n- The real issue is that everything keeps getting dumped into the Feishu table without any clear workflow for what gets tested next or how to actually move products through to testing\n\nI need to build an SOP that actually solves this: distinguish between products that are tracked versus products ready for testing, and create a separate pipeline so we can actually follow up on what's been tested versus what's still in the observation phase.\n","thinkingSignature":"6445b1afb547b584f0206f7e3bb641941b1c79e6c6f5b66d795a9670ca7cecaa"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n理解了。你的核心痛点是：\n\n1. **选了品 ≠ 能测品**，两者混在一起没有区分\n2. **进了表格 ≠ 被追踪**，没有后续动作\n3. **SOP 要简化**，不要复杂验证，要简单直接\n\n---\n\n我来梳理一个清晰的 SOP，先看一下你飞书多维表的结构：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_171c7bb05c7b4f7188887ff6","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56689,"output":359,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17809093