{"type":"message","id":"cc3ee5fc","parentId":"52df5e95","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:38:33.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config shows no `mcp.servers` configured at all. There's no Sorftime MCP server in the config. So the tools `tiktok_product_trend` and `ali1688_similar_product` are not available - they're either:\n1. From a Sorftime MCP that was previously configured but removed\n2. Or the user is looking at a list of available MCP tools from somewhere else\n\nThe current reality: **Sorftime MCP is NOT configured in the system**. There's no `mcp.servers` section in the config at all. The Sorftime API calls we've been making were via `exec curl` commands, not MCP tools.\n\nSo the user is asking about two MCP tools that show as \"未配置\" (not configured) - meaning they don't exist in the current MCP setup.\n\n\nI should be direct about this: Sorftime isn't set up as an MCP server at all, which is likely why those tools aren't showing up. The API calls we've been using came from direct curl commands, not from MCP. The user seems to want a more streamlined workflow with better tracking and clearer next steps, so I should focus on understanding what they're actually trying to accomplish rather than just explaining the configuration gap.","thinkingSignature":"d44bd05ec9af8796c8507b9a47650480e289c01542f4286ca79845703261bd5b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**配置里根本没有 Sorftime MCP Server**——`mcp.servers` 是空的。\n\n那两个工具显示\"未配置\"，是因为它们根本不在系统里。我们之前一直在用的是 **`exec curl` 直调 Sorftime REST API**，不是 MCP。\n\n---\n\n现在说正事——你的失望我理解。核心问题不是工具，是**流程断了**：\n\n| 问题 | 现状 | 应该 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 进了表格 ≠ 被追踪 | 所有品混在一起 | 要区分「待测品」vs「已测品」|\n| 选了品 ≠ 能测品 | 只看数据指标 | 要有1688货源确认|\n| 没有后续 | 每周选10个进表格 | 要知道哪些真的下了首单|\n\n---\n\n我来重整一个简洁有效的 SOP，核心两个表：\n\n**① 选品池**（现在这个）—— 所有扫描到的潜力品\n**② 测品追踪**（新建）—— 进了1688货源确认、下了首单的品\n\n**每周目标：10个品进测品池，3个品真实下首单测品**\n\n---\n\n先让我看一下现在表格里有多少数据：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c51e93611e5c43da9403fad6","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd","table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT","page_size":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15196,"output":569,"cacheRead":60480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780922306531,"responseId":"0675eac3a504fd470c9cb0b7446800f5"}}
