10 chiếc lược chải tóc chống tĩnh điện","type":"text"}],"增长率":-26,"推荐等级":"C","月销量":11277,"站点":"越南","行动建议":"观望","选品来源":["Sorftime-TK数据"],"采集状态":"已采集"},"record_id":"recvlu1nyfL7lz"},{"fields":{"1688价格(CNY)":3.6,"1688同款链接":{"link":"https://detail.1688.com/offer/853197961101.html","text":"在逃公主大蝴蝶结头饰1688","type":"url"},"三级类目":"发夹","产品连接":{"link":"https://www.tiktok.com/@shop/product/1730776096325864030","text":"TK产品链接","type":"url"},"利润率(%)":66,"售价（本地货币）":29980,"商品名称":[{"text":"KẹP TóC Bong Bóng Búi Củ Tỏi, KẹP Tóc Nữ Phong Cách Thời Trang Women Voi Hoa Voan","type":"text"}],"增长率":180,"推荐等级":"S级","日期":1772121600000,"月销量":2309,"站点":"越南","选品来源":["Sorftime-TK数据"],"预估利润":19817},"record_id":"recvlDHsUVRdP8"}],"has_more":true,"page_token":"***","total":31},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780922317144}}
{"type":"message","id":"300de4da","parentId":"b616390c","timestamp":"2026-06-08T12:38:45.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so there are 31 records total. Looking at the data:\n\n1. The first record doesn't have 1688 filled in (only 25902 monthly sales, no other data)\n2. Some records have 1688 links and good profit margins (31%, 17%, 66%)\n3. Some have negative profit (-5%)\n4. The采集状态 varies: some \"已采集\", some missing\n5. 行动建议: some \"正常采购首单30-50件\", some \"观望\"\n\nThe user is right - there's no tracking of what actually happened after selection. It's just data in, data out.\n\n\nNow I need to restructure this into a proper SOP. The current table mixes everything together without a clear workflow, so I'll design two distinct phases: first, a \"候选池\" where new products enter and get filtered down to the top 10 weekly based on trend potential and profit margins, and second, a \"测品池\" for confirmed products with actual 1688 sourcing that are ready for test orders.\n\nI'll present this workflow clearly to the user and ask for confirmation before implementing it in the spreadsheet.","thinkingSignature":"a09c9f3aa30617df84951fd0e2be3ab1a915db774873d082b74eb81b51daaaff"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n表格里现在有 **31条记录**，看了下数据质量——问题很明显：\n\n- 有的品利润是负的（-5%），行动建议写\"观望\"也进了表\n- 有采集状态的、有没采集状态的，混在一起\n- 进了表之后没有任何1688货源跟进记录\n- 没有\"下了首单\"vs\"还在观望\"的状态区分\n\n---\n\n**新 SOP 框架，两张表分开跑：**\n\n### ① 选品池（改造现在的表）\n**每周更新一次**，扫TK趋势 → 只放满足以下条件的品：\n- 月销量 ≥ 1000\n- 增长率 ≥ 30%（24h或7d）\n- 利润率 ≥ 20%\n- 有1688同款（能找到货源）\n- 不是负利润在观望的品\n\n**新增字段：** 审核状态（✅进入测品池 / ❌淘汰 / ⏳待确认1688）\n\n---\n\n### ② 测品追踪（新建表）\n**目标：每周进10个品，真实下3单**\n\n字段：\n- 商品名称 / TikTok链接 / 1688链接\n- 首单时间 / 首单数量 / 首单金额\n- 测品结果（爆/平/死）\n- 决定：加仓 / 维持 / 放弃\n- 备注\n\n---\n\n**每周选品流程：**\n1. 扫趋势 → 候选10个 → 确认1688货源\n2. 有货源的进测品池\n3. 你实际下了首单 → 更新测品追踪表\n4. 测品结果出来后 → 决定加仓还是放弃\n\n---\n\n你觉得这个框架可以吗？可以的话我就开始改造飞书表格。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1672,"output":586,"cacheRead":75904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780922317832,"responseId":"0675eacee81baf8ffaf926078ffe08a2"}}
